1
00:00:48,792 --> 00:00:51,125
When Mrs. McBing was in labour…

2
00:00:51,250 --> 00:00:54,000
A pan appeared in the sky.

3
00:00:55,042 --> 00:00:58,208
It flied along Garden Street…

4
00:00:58,375 --> 00:01:04,750
Turned left, and stopped
at the Beef ball King.

5
00:01:05,750 --> 00:01:06,958
Correction:

6
00:01:07,083 --> 00:01:10,042
It first arrived at the Market Building…

7
00:01:10,333 --> 00:01:13,292
Lingered a bit…Correction:

8
00:01:13,375 --> 00:01:18,458
It flied over the railway, turned right…

9
00:01:18,583 --> 00:01:23,792
And headed directly for the Bazaar.

10
00:01:23,917 --> 00:01:25,708
It flied on…

11
00:01:25,875 --> 00:01:29,042
At last coming into the maternity ward.

12
00:01:29,208 --> 00:01:32,500
There, on the right hand side of
Mrs. McBing.

13
00:01:32,792 --> 00:01:35,083
Correction: Left hand side.

14
00:01:35,250 --> 00:01:37,708
The pan stayed.

15
00:01:38,167 --> 00:01:40,167
Mrs. McBing,
convinced that this was a miracle,

16
00:01:40,667 --> 00:01:43,292
Made a wish…

17
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:47,167
Thinking of her soon-to-be-born son.

18
00:01:47,333 --> 00:01:50,458
Please make him
a clever and smart boy!

19
00:01:50,708 --> 00:01:53,833
The pan didn't seem to hear her words.

20
00:01:53,958 --> 00:01:56,167
So Mrs. McBing amended her wish:

21
00:01:56,333 --> 00:01:58,875
Or make him a smart businessman?

22
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,542
Or maybe…

23
00:02:00,667 --> 00:02:02,542
Or make him really handsome.

24
00:02:02,708 --> 00:02:06,042
As handsome as Chow Yun Fat or
Tony Leung!

25
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:12,042
The pan didn't respond.

26
00:02:12,167 --> 00:02:13,583
Mrs. McBing, in panic…

27
00:02:13,792 --> 00:02:17,667
Made a final amendment:

28
00:02:18,042 --> 00:02:21,708
Her boy needed not to be
smart or handsome

29
00:02:21,875 --> 00:02:24,917
As long as luck be with him!

30
00:02:25,958 --> 00:02:29,542
It's nice to depend on oneself…

31
00:02:29,667 --> 00:02:31,917
But luck is essential still.

32
00:02:32,167 --> 00:02:35,500
Of course Chow and Leung are
lucky guys…

33
00:02:36,292 --> 00:02:38,875
But then they are smart too!

34
00:02:42,208 --> 00:02:44,542
Finally, the pan dropped to the floor…

35
00:02:44,708 --> 00:02:49,458
Mrs. McBing,
believing her wish granted…

36
00:02:49,583 --> 00:02:52,417
Thought that was magnificent!

37
00:02:52,583 --> 00:02:54,167
But what had the pan granted her?

38
00:02:54,958 --> 00:02:57,375
A smart boy? A lucky boy?

39
00:02:57,500 --> 00:02:59,417
Or a Chow look-alike?

40
00:03:00,667 --> 00:03:02,708
To commemorate this, Mrs. McBing…

41
00:03:03,208 --> 00:03:06,250
Decided to name her son McNificient.

42
00:03:07,250 --> 00:03:09,750
No! It's better to be humble!

43
00:03:09,958 --> 00:03:11,958
I'll name him McDull!

44
00:03:12,167 --> 00:03:13,292
Dear all…

45
00:03:13,458 --> 00:03:16,208
I am the boy, no more McNificient…

46
00:03:16,875 --> 00:03:18,542
I'm McDull!

47
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:43,375
"My School"

48
00:04:43,583 --> 00:04:45,083
Oh dear,

49
00:04:45,250 --> 00:04:47,083
your calves have grown strong.

50
00:04:47,208 --> 00:04:48,875
I've been desperately…

51
00:04:49,042 --> 00:04:50,500
looking for a school!

52
00:04:50,833 --> 00:04:52,667
Why not try the one…

53
00:04:52,792 --> 00:04:54,667
at the Emporium?

54
00:04:54,792 --> 00:04:57,083
The Spring Flower Kindergarten?

55
00:04:57,292 --> 00:04:59,833
Yeah! The one at the junction…

56
00:05:00,042 --> 00:05:01,667
Right next to Silver City Food Mall.

57
00:05:01,833 --> 00:05:03,833
The Spring Flower Kindergarten!

58
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:08,208
Only 10 minutes walk from
the MTR Station!

59
00:05:08,333 --> 00:05:11,625
Spring Flower Kindergarten,
good environment…

60
00:05:11,750 --> 00:05:14,208
With white teachers for English class!

61
00:05:14,333 --> 00:05:16,125
White teachers for English class?

62
00:05:16,250 --> 00:05:16,958
Yeah!

63
00:05:17,125 --> 00:05:22,417
Spring Flower offers white teachers!

64
00:05:31,292 --> 00:05:35,958
"We are all happy children…"

65
00:05:36,042 --> 00:05:40,917
"We sing everyday!"

66
00:05:41,042 --> 00:05:45,625
"We learn as we grow…"

67
00:05:45,750 --> 00:05:50,792
"We are the flowers of spring!"

68
00:05:51,833 --> 00:05:54,083
This piggy kid in a rabbit outfit…

69
00:05:54,292 --> 00:05:58,625
Who doesn't look the least
like Chow or Leung…

70
00:05:58,792 --> 00:06:01,167
That's me, McDull.

71
00:06:02,292 --> 00:06:04,000
This is my kindergarten.

72
00:06:04,875 --> 00:06:06,542
The headmaster came from
the countryside…

73
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,875
As a result, he speaks with an accent.

74
00:06:09,083 --> 00:06:10,208
For many years…

75
00:06:10,458 --> 00:06:12,875
I had difficulty hearing him.

76
00:06:14,625 --> 00:06:17,833
- Tart!    - Tart!

77
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:23,583
- Duck dumpling!    - Duck dumpling!

78
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:29,792
- The 97 Rule…    - The 97 Rule…

79
00:06:29,958 --> 00:06:33,083
Shall be replaced by the 98 Rule!

80
00:06:33,250 --> 00:06:38,792
Shall be replaced by the 98 Rule!

81
00:06:39,167 --> 00:06:40,667
Good, children!

82
00:06:40,833 --> 00:06:43,208
We are sharing an important issue…

83
00:06:43,375 --> 00:06:45,000
this morning:

84
00:06:45,375 --> 00:06:48,417
Children, have you handed in
the school fee?

85
00:06:48,583 --> 00:06:50,792
Yes!

86
00:06:50,958 --> 00:06:54,375
Great! Now move to class.

87
00:06:57,875 --> 00:07:00,417
You might conclude that
this is a shabby school.

88
00:07:00,583 --> 00:07:03,125
But, for me and my mates…

89
00:07:03,708 --> 00:07:06,625
This is the most beautiful paradise!

90
00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:10,000
…Also, there is Miss Chan.

91
00:07:10,125 --> 00:07:12,833
Who adores us in
her absent-minded way.

92
00:07:13,917 --> 00:07:16,083
Also, she is a Faye Wong wannabe.

93
00:07:16,375 --> 00:07:18,708
Actually, Kelly Chan will do!

