- Goosie!    - Present!

115
00:08:08,125 --> 00:08:09,458
- Goosie!    - Present!

116
00:08:09,625 --> 00:08:11,375
Have I missed anyone?

117
00:08:11,542 --> 00:08:13,458
McDull!

118
00:08:14,250 --> 00:08:15,667
McDull!

119
00:08:16,667 --> 00:08:18,208
McDull!

120
00:08:18,708 --> 00:08:20,000
McDull!

121
00:08:20,167 --> 00:08:22,167
Hey, I don't understand…

122
00:08:22,333 --> 00:08:23,625
I keep feeling that…

123
00:08:23,792 --> 00:08:27,625
Someone is calling me.

124
00:08:28,583 --> 00:08:30,500
Don't think that I've been daydreaming.

125
00:08:30,875 --> 00:08:33,667
I was contemplating something academic:

126
00:08:33,833 --> 00:08:36,917
How does this universe work?

127
00:08:37,542 --> 00:08:39,833
I mean, I ate 6 oranges that morning…

128
00:08:40,042 --> 00:08:44,542
And my stomach wouldn't stop.

129
00:08:44,708 --> 00:08:47,125
Then I ate 3 bananas this morning.

130
00:08:47,292 --> 00:08:50,375
Again my stomach wouldn't stop…

131
00:08:50,542 --> 00:08:52,958
It just wouldn't stop!

132
00:08:53,250 --> 00:08:57,083
How are these two things related?

133
00:08:57,958 --> 00:09:00,500
There are so many things that
I don't understand.

134
00:09:00,667 --> 00:09:02,292
But I am not afraid.

135
00:09:02,375 --> 00:09:04,667
One day, when I finish kindergarten…

136
00:09:04,833 --> 00:09:08,000
I shall move up…

137
00:09:08,125 --> 00:09:09,750
And get my degree.

138
00:09:09,875 --> 00:09:11,167
When I graduate from university, I know…

139
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:13,292
I shall understand everything!

140
00:09:13,458 --> 00:09:14,583
And then…

141
00:09:15,125 --> 00:09:17,292
I will buy my mother a house!

142
00:09:21,083 --> 00:09:24,125
Our headmaster runs a tea stand…

143
00:09:24,292 --> 00:09:27,375
Which we kids frequent after class.

144
00:09:27,583 --> 00:09:30,125
- Fishball noodle, please.
- No noodle left.

145
00:09:30,417 --> 00:09:33,917
- Fishball rice noodle then.
- No fishball left.

146
00:09:34,083 --> 00:09:37,792
- Chicken wing noodle then.
- No noodle left.

147
00:09:38,958 --> 00:09:41,833
- How about fishball congee?
- No fishball left.

148
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,417
Nothing left today?

149
00:09:43,833 --> 00:09:46,625
- How about beef noodle?
- No noodle left.

150
00:09:46,917 --> 00:09:47,958
Again?

151
00:09:48,167 --> 00:09:51,708
- Fried chicken wing with fishball…
- No fishball left.

152
00:09:51,917 --> 00:09:55,333
Hey, fishball and noodle are both gone…

153
00:09:55,542 --> 00:09:58,917
You can't combine them with other things.

154
00:10:00,375 --> 00:10:02,125
Can't combine them?

155
00:10:02,458 --> 00:10:04,917
- A bowl of fishball then.
- No fishball left.

156
00:10:05,083 --> 00:10:06,667
- A bowl of noodle?
- No noodle left.

157
00:10:07,792 --> 00:10:08,708
By now…

158
00:10:08,875 --> 00:10:11,250
you can probably tell how smart I am.

159
00:10:11,583 --> 00:10:13,958
Nothing worried me, all things were fine.

160
00:10:14,292 --> 00:10:17,000
No fishball left? Let's get some noodle.

161
00:10:17,167 --> 00:10:20,042
Shoot, Dull!

162
00:10:23,833 --> 00:10:25,625
Watching myself grow and grow…

163
00:10:26,333 --> 00:10:27,625
Everyday…

164
00:10:27,833 --> 00:10:29,292
I feel full of strength!

165
00:10:29,458 --> 00:10:30,833
The world is beautiful!

166
00:10:33,875 --> 00:10:36,750
There is a song Miss Chan loves…

167
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,375
Which I always want to learn…

168
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:41,667
But it just comes out different.

169
00:10:41,792 --> 00:10:44,375
You mean
"All Things Bright and Beautiful"?

170
00:10:44,542 --> 00:10:46,375
Yes, all are fine!

171
00:10:46,458 --> 00:10:47,708
All things on earth…

172
00:10:47,833 --> 00:10:50,375
They are fine!!

173
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:45,375
"My Mother"

174
00:11:54,708 --> 00:11:56,500
1,2,3,4,5,6,7…

175
00:11:56,625 --> 00:11:57,792
No pain no gain!

176
00:11:57,958 --> 00:12:01,417
Monday till Sunday… No pain no gain!

177
00:12:01,792 --> 00:12:03,750
The middle-aged swine is Mrs. McBing,

178
00:12:03,875 --> 00:12:05,750
my mother…

179
00:12:06,083 --> 00:12:07,500
A brilliant woman…

180
00:12:07,708 --> 00:12:09,833
carrying the world!

